SP_ID [integer] = shape ID nom_arr [character] = name of area described by shape can_area [number] = ? what is can? muni_area [integer] = why is this an integer? perc_co [number] = ? sp [integer] = number of species observed in shape area? Is this a model or data? rrar [number] = ? abun [integer] = abundance of something? trunof [number] = ? stand_run [number]= something about water runoff? polrem [number]= polution remediation? stand_pol [number]= standing polution? carbon [number] = what about carbon? stand_car [number] = why is this a decimal if the unit is a car? is this number of cars that park in a shape? Sequestrat[number] = sequestering rats? stand_seq [number] = standing sequestration of something. Evap [number] = evaporation from trees? stand_evap [number]= standing evaporation? evaporation from standing vegetation? meaning seasonal? mtl [factor] = in MTL city limits or data provided by MTL? or other? order [factor] = ? cancarbon2 [number]= what is special about the can designation? Are the data from canadian federal sources? canrunoffa[number]= canseq2 [number] = canpoll [number] = what is poll?
